<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Request Payment</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/fonts.css" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: #808080; padding: 30px">
    <table style="width: 600px; padding: 30px; margin: auto;background-color: #fff;">
      <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center">
          <!-- <img src="" height="80px"> -->
        </td>
        <td>
          <!-- <h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 30px;"></h1> -->
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000">
        <td style="color: #2d2d2d; padding-bottom: 10px">
          <h4 style="margin: 0px">
            A Merchant PlutoPe user <%= requestFrom %> has requested you (<%=
            fromUser %>) to send <%= amount %> <%= currency %> to his Stellar
            account: <%= publicKey %>
          </h4>

          <p style="font-size: 15px">
            If you don't have a Merchant PlutoPe account, please signup here.
          </p>

          <p style="font-size: 15px">
            Stellar is an open-source, distributed payments infrastructure. XLM
            (Stellar Lumens) is a currency of Stellar network.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 15px">
            If you don't know <%= requestFrom %> or haven't expected payment
            requests — please ignore this message.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 15px">
            If you wish to make the payment requested, scan this QR code with
            your Stellar wallet:
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 15px">
            If you wish to make the payment through web page <a href="<%= shareLink %>">click here</a> to get the link.
          </p>

          <div style="text-align: center">
            <img src="<%= qrLink %>" height="170px" alt="QR Code" />
          </div>
          <h4 style="margin: 0px; margin-top: 10px">Best Regards,</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0px">Merchant PlutoPe Team</p>

          <tr>
            <td
              style="
                border-top: 1px solid #cedce1;
                color: #aab7bc;
                font-size: 12px;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 5px;
                line-height: 20px;
              "
            >
              Copyright © 2024,
              <a style="color: #0a6ac5" target="_blank" href="https://merchant.plutope.app/">merchantplutope.com</a>
              <br />
              All rights reserved.
              <br />
              <!-- <a style="color: #0a6ac5" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a>
              |
              <a style="color: #0a6ac5" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a>
              <br /> -->
            </td>
          </tr>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
